reviewText: Hi,I take longer time to understand the instructions and I need more time to complete the GIMP basic course.  How can I go back to the instructions I haven't got? Time limit is not fair to everyone. Violette Paré

The tutor talks very monotonic i think its a motivation decreasing factor.The course is extremely short and you will learn just the basic basics i suggest not to waste your time here and enroll in some other longer course.
